  <h1>SifterSearch Documentation</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">AI-powered search for the world's sacred texts</p>

  <p>
    SifterSearch is an intelligent search system designed to help scholars, seekers, and researchers
    explore sacred texts from the world's religious traditions. Built on a multi-agent AI architecture,
    it goes beyond simple keyword matching to understand the deeper meaning behind your questions.
  </p>

  <h2>What Makes SifterSearch Different</h2>

  <p>Traditional search engines find words. SifterSearch finds <strong>meaning</strong>.</p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Semantic Understanding</strong> - Understands concepts, not just keywords. Search for "detachment from material things" and find passages about spiritual freedom, even if they don't use those exact words.</li>
    <li><strong>Cross-Tradition Discovery</strong> - Explore how different religions approach similar themes. Find connections between Baha'i writings, Buddhist sutras, and Christian mystics.</li>
    <li><strong>AI-Powered Analysis</strong> - Each search result is scored, summarized, and highlighted by AI to show you why it's relevant to your query.</li>
    <li><strong>Scholarly Focus</strong> - Built for serious study with proper citations, source attribution, and access to original texts.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Core Features</h2>

  <h3>Hybrid Search</h3>
  <p>
    Combines traditional keyword search with semantic vector search for best-of-both-worlds results.
    Find exact quotes when you need them, or explore conceptually related passages.
  </p>

  <h3>Multi-Agent System</h3>
  <p>
    Under the hood, specialized AI agents collaborate to understand your query, design search strategies,
    analyze results, and present findings. <a href="/docs/agents">Learn more about our agents &rarr;</a>
  </p>

  <h3>Comprehensive Library</h3>
  <p>
    Access thousands of documents spanning major world religions, with special depth in Baha'i writings,
    pilgrim notes, and interfaith literature. <a href="/docs/library">Explore the library &rarr;</a>
  </p>

  <h3>Developer API</h3>
  <p>
    Build your own applications on top of SifterSearch with our public REST API. Full AI analysis,
    filtering, and rate limiting included. <a href="/docs/api">View API docs &rarr;</a>
  </p>

  <h2>Quick Start</h2>

  <ol>
    <li><strong>Ask a question</strong> - Type naturally: "What does Baha'u'llah say about justice?"</li>
    <li><strong>Review results</strong> - Each passage shows its relevance score and key phrases highlighted</li>
    <li><strong>Explore deeper</strong> - Click any result to see the full context and document</li>
    <li><strong>Refine your search</strong> - Filter by religion, collection, or time period</li>
  </ol>

